I used to run this with [Sign in Blood](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sign in Blood). I used the sign to refill opponents hand when they had no cards left, followed by a [mind rot](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mind rot) on the same turn.  

@Troll Beserk.  

It won games in kitchen table top. The strategy was discard in general, and sign in blood lategame to take advantage of multiple megrims. It was quite powerful for the environment I was playing in.
